OL,3,CMum fearing for son's health in home
OL,4,Cwith black mould
OL,6,FA tenant at a council property in
OL,7,FCarmarthenshire who has been calling
OL,8,Fon the local authority to repair damp
OL,9,Fand mould problems at her home says
OL,10,Fher pleas have "fallen on deaf ears."
OL,12,FKatie Jones moved into the two-bed
OL,13,Fhouse in Llanllwni back in August
OL,14,F2020, looking forward to a fresh start
OL,15,Fwith her newborn baby.
OL,17,FHowever, her hopes and dreams quickly
OL,18,Fturned into an ordeal during her first
OL,19,Fwinter at the property, when damp and
OL,20,Fmould started appearing.
