OL,6,FKatie says she had long been asking
OL,7,Ffor help from Carmarthenshire County
OL,8,FCouncil, who own the property, but
OL,9,Fclaims nothing was done until a
OL,10,Fbedroom ceiling partially collapsed in
OL,11,FOctober 2022.
OL,13,FThe night of the ceiling collapse,
OL,14,FKatie says her son, Mason, who would
OL,15,Fhave been two-years-old at the time
OL,16,Fhad only just left the bedroom before
OL,17,Fthe ceiling collapsed.
