OL,3,CMum fearing for son's health in home
OL,4,Cwith black mould
OL,6,FImmediately after the collapse in
OL,7,FOctober 2022, the local authority
OL,8,Ffitted a wooden board to cover the
OL,9,Fhole, with scaffolding also erected
OL,10,Foutside the property.
OL,12,FAt the time of filming, Katie told us
OL,13,Fit had been over a year since the
OL,14,Flocal authority had last inspected the
OL,15,Fproperty and hadn't heard back from
OL,16,Fthem since.
OL,18,FHer greatest concern has been the
OL,19,Fimpact it's been having on Mason, who
OL,20,Fhas a congenital heart condition.
