OL,3,CMum fearing for son's health in home
OL,4,Cwith black mould
OL,6,F"I've spoken to multiple doctors and
OL,7,Fhealth care professionals about the
OL,8,Fsituation," Katie told ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,10,F"I've shown them photos of the state
OL,11,Fof the house and a few of them have
OL,12,Fsent letters to the council stressing
OL,13,Ftheir concerns about the fact Mason is
OL,14,Fbasically being forced to live in
OL,15,Fthese conditions.
OL,17,F"From what I understand nobody's heard
OL,18,Fanything back and I certainly haven't
OL,19,Fheard anything back. He's a poorly
OL,20,Flittle boy, anyway. So, I want them to
OL,21,Ffix it, that's all."
