OL,6,FITV News took its footage to Tim
OL,7,FDavies, a qualified RICS chartered
OL,8,Fsurveyor to get his thoughts on the
OL,9,Fcondition of the property.
OL,11,F"I've got to be honest, that is pretty
OL,12,Fhorrifying and to think that people
OL,13,Fare actually living in that, living in
OL,14,Fthis sort of environment is extremely
OL,15,Fworrying," he said.
OL,17,F"Black mould can cause no end of
OL,18,Fproblems with your health and to be in
OL,19,Fthat environment with this amount of
OL,20,Fdampness and mould is very concerning.
