OL,6,F"From what I can see, they've put the
OL,7,Fscaffolding up but it doesn't look
OL,8,Flike they've done anything else. I'm
OL,9,Fnot privy to their investigatory
OL,10,Fmethods and what surveyors they use
OL,11,Fwhether they use in house or
OL,12,Fconsultants.
OL,14,F"But somebody really needs to go up
OL,15,Fthere with experience for matters like
OL,16,Fthis and it is not rocket science."
