OL,6,FIn a statement, Cllr Linda Evans,
OL,7,FDeputy Leader and Cabinet Member for
OL,8,FHomes at Carmarthenshire County said:
OL,9,F"We recognise the delay in undertaking
OL,10,Fworks at the property. It falls below
OL,11,Fthe service we aim to be providing
OL,12,Fand, for this, we would like to
OL,13,Freiterate our apology to Ms Jones, as
OL,14,Four tenant.
OL,16,F"We have made contact with Ms Jones
OL,17,Fand work has already started and a
OL,18,Fprogramme of works has been agreed in
OL,19,Fconjunction with the tenant.
