OL,6,F"Alternative accommodation has also
OL,7,Fbeen offered whilst the outstanding
OL,8,Fworks are completed.
OL,10,F"Finally, we along with many providers
OL,11,Fare trying to increase our maintenance
OL,12,Fcapacity with a view to complete more
OL,13,Frepairs both in house and with local
OL,14,Fcontractors.
OL,16,F"As always in these cases we will
OL,17,Fcarry out a review of Ms Jones's case
OL,18,Fto ensure any issues identified are
OL,19,Fnot repeated elsewhere."
